item.title: Please can someone help me ? [PI]
item.dc:creator: @Doobage Doobage
item.description:
@Doobage wrote:

Test it with hamachi first. see if it works. If it works, it’s a port forwarding issue or a configuration issue.

make sure Server ip is set to a no-ip and port is 43594 or w.e port u want it to be and your client is the same.

Make sure your not port forwarding from the firewall and ur port forwarding from 192.168.1.1 or w.e your Router’s IP address is.
